jSMIparser
Copyright (c) 2026, jSMIparser contributors

This project is an independent Java reimplementation that targets output
compatibility with pysmi's ASN.1 MIB -> JSON pipeline (the JsonCodeGen
output schema and several documented behavioural quirks). No pysmi source
code is included or redistributed; the grammar and Java implementation
here are original.

